{% render 'section-new-faq-1-styles-min' %}
<div class="section-container">
                <h2 class="faq-title hero__overlay-title section-title has-animated">
                    Featured Questions
                </h2>
            <div class="new-faq_wrapp">
                <div class="new-faq_item">
                    <div class="new-faq_item-title">
                        <p class="font-title">
                            Who can use LegitGrails authentication service?
                        </p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)"  class="font-title">
                            +
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="new-faq_item-text">
                        <p class="font-description">
                            Our authentication service is available to any individual or business who wishes to verify the authenticity of a product, regardless of their location.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="new-faq_item">
                    <div class="new-faq_item-title">
                        <p class="font-title">
                            How does LegitGrails {{ product.title }} work?
                        </p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="font-title">
                            +
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="new-faq_item-text">
                        <p class="font-description">
                            Our {{ product.title }} service uses a combination of human expertise and advanced technology to authenticate branded items. You must upload photos of your product from various angles, and our team of experts will analyse the details to determine if the product is authentic or counterfeit. If any additional information is needed, our friendly team will reach out to you.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="new-faq_item">
                    <div class="new-faq_item-title">
                        <p class="font-title">
                            What sets LegitGrails {{ product.title }} apart from similar services?
                        </p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="font-title">
                            +
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="new-faq_item-text">
                        <p class="font-description">
                            Our {{ product.title }} service is highly accurate, fast, and has excellent customer support. Our team of authentication experts has over six years of experience in the field, ensuring that each item is thoroughly verified by a minimum of two experts. We provide detailed reports of our findings, a free authenticity certificate for every verified item and ongoing customer service to ensure transparency and trust throughout the process.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="new-faq_item">
                    <div class="new-faq_item-title">
                        <p class="font-title">
                            Which photos should I upload for authentication?
                        </p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="font-title">
                            +
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="new-faq_item-text">
                        <p class="font-description">
                            To ensure the best possible authentication results, we recommend that users upload clear and detailed photos of the product from various angles, which are listed when you press 'Upload photos' on this page. The photos should be well-lit and show the product in its entirety, without any obstructions or reflections. Check out <a href="https://legitgrails.frontkb.com/en/categories/604802-general-photos">Photo Instructions</a> to find clear examples for each detail.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="new-faq_item">
                    <div class="new-faq_item-title">
                        <p class="font-title">
                            How long does the authentication process take?
                        </p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="font-title">
                            +
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="new-faq_item-text">
                        <p class="font-description">
                            We prioritise delivering fast and precise results to our users. As soon as our analysis is complete, we will notify you promptly. You have the option to choose your preferred turnaround time before submitting your item for authentication, ensuring that we meet your needs.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
              <div class="new-faq_item">
                    <div class="new-faq_item-title">
                        <p class="font-title">
                            How precise is LegitGrails {{ product.title }}?
                        </p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="font-title">
                            +
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="new-faq_item-text">
                        <p class="font-description">
                            At LegitGrails, we pride ourselves on providing highly accurate authentication results with a success rate of over 99%. Our team of experts utilises advanced tools and visual analysis to thoroughly examine your product and identify any potential signs of counterfeiting. You can trust us to deliver a reliable and trustworthy {{ product.title }}.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
              <div class="new-faq_item">
                    <div class="new-faq_item-title">
                        <p class="font-title">
                            Is it possible to have my model authenticated by LegitGrails?
                        </p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="font-title">
                            +
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="new-faq_item-text">
                        <p class="font-description">
                            We offer authentication services for a wide variety of branded products, such as handbags, footwear, clothing, and accessories, and cover most popular models. In the rare case that we are unable to provide authentication services for your specific item, our team will promptly inform you and offer any assistance that we can.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
              <div class="new-faq_item">
                    <div class="new-faq_item-title">
                        <p class="font-title">
                            What happens if my item is deemed fake?
                        </p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="font-title">
                            +
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="new-faq_item-text">
                        <p class="font-description">
                            In the unfortunate event that your item is deemed counterfeit by LegitGrails, we will provide you with a comprehensive report of our findings and inform you of the result. We also offer <a href="https://legitgrails.com/products/refundgrails">consultancy services</a> that may assist you in recovering your money if you're in a dispute with the seller. You can rely on us to provide support and guidance throughout the entire authentication process.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
              <div class="new-faq_item">
                    <div class="new-faq_item-title">
                        <p class="font-title">
                            What if I have additional questions or concerns about the service?
                        </p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="font-title">
                            +
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="new-faq_item-text">
                        <p class="font-description">
                            If you have additional questions or concerns about the service, please feel free to contact our customer support team. We are available 24/7 to assist you with any inquiries, feedback, or issues you may encounter. You can reach us through our live chat on the website, our email <a href="mailto:info@legitgrails.com">info@legitgrails.com</a>, or visit our <a href="https://legitgrails.frontkb.com/en">Help Center</a>. We will respond as soon as possible.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
  <div class="new-faq_bottom font-title">
      <p>Have more questions? Visit our <a href="https://legitgrails.frontkb.com/en">Help Center</a></p>
  </div>
        </div>


<script src="{{ 'new-faq-item-click.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>

{% schema %}
  {
    "name": "New FAQ 1",
    "class": "new-faq",
    "tag": "section",
    "presets": [
    {
      "name": "New FAQ 1"
    }
  ]
  }
{% endschema %}